  %body.enable-animations.enable-preloader
    #document.document
      / HEADER
      %header#header.header-section.section.section-dark.navbar.navbar-fixed-top
        .container-fluid
          .navbar-header.navbar-left
            / RESPONSIVE MENU BUTTON
            %button.navbar-toggle{"data-target" => "#navigation", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :type => "button"}
              %span.sr-only Toggle navigation
              %span.icon-bar
              %span.icon-bar
              %span.icon-bar
            / HEADER LOGO
            %a.navbar-logo.navbar-brand.anchor-link{:href => "#hero"}
              {{ 'logos/header-logo.png' | theme_image_tag: "alt:Myrick" }}
          %nav#navigation.navigation.navbar-collapse.collapse.navbar-right
            / NAVIGATION LINKS
            %ul#header-nav.nav.navbar-nav
              %li
                %a.hidden{:href => "#hero"} Top
              %li
                %a{:href => "#about"} About
              %li
                %a{:href => "#benefits"} Products
              %li
                %a{:href => "#how-it-works"} How it Works
              %li
                %a{:href => "#testimonial-slider"} Testimonial
              / HEADER ACTION BUTTON
              %li.header-action-button
                %a.btn.btn-primary{:href => "#contact-maps"} Contact Us
      / HERO
      %section#hero.hero-section.hero-layout-simple.hero-fullscreen.section.section-dark
        .section-background
          / IMAGE BACKGROUND
          .section-background-image.parallax{"data-stellar-ratio" => "0.4"}
            {{ 'backgrounds/section1_background.jpg' | theme_image_tag: 'class:opacity-07' }}
        .container
          .hero-content
            .hero-content-inner
              .row
                .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
                  .hero-heading.text-center{"data-animation" => "fadeIn"}
                    %h1.hero-title
                      {{ 'logos/myrick_logo_white.png' | theme_image_tag }}
                    %p.hero-tagline Where Ideas Come to Life
                  %p.hero-buttons.text-center
                    %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-default{:href => "#about"} Learn More
                    %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary{:href => "#contact-maps"} Contact Us
        / HERO START LINK
        %a.hero-start-link.anchor-link{:href => "#headline"}
          %span.fa.fa-angle-double-down
      / HEADLINE
      %section#headline.headline-section.section-gray.section
        .container
          %h2.section-heading.text-center.hidden Tagline
          .row
            .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
              %p.headline-text
                Status quo doesn't work for us. Going above and beyond for our
                customers is not just a saying; it's the way we live. Our
                mission is to provide the most memorable experience for our
                customers and theirs.
      / DESCRIPTION
      %section#about.about-section.section
        .container
          %h2.section-heading.text-center About Myrick Consulting
          .about-row.row
            / DESCRIPTION IMAGE
            .about-image.col-md-6{"data-animation" => "fadeIn"}
              {{ 'contents/about_image.jpg' | theme_image_tag: "alt: Description Image" }}
            / DESCRIPTION TEXT
            .about-text.col-md-6
              %p.lead 
                We are quality and customer centric enabling us to build great
                relationships with our customers and within our community.
              %p
                Myrick Consulting is an advertising company that specializes in
                print and digital advertising. We Partner with businesses to
                develop, execute, manage, and analyze your advertising
                campaigns. Myrick provides quality print products, digital
                advertising, websites, hosting and may other services. We are
                quality and customer centric enabling us to build great
                relationships with our customers and within our community.
      / Products
      %section#benefits.benefits-section.section-gray.section
        .container
          %h2.section-heading.text-center Products
          .benefits-row.row
            / BENEFIT 1
            .col-sm-6.col-md-4
              .benefit
                %span.benefit-icon.fa.fa-area-chart{"data-animation" => "bounceIn"}
                %h4.benefit-title Marketing Strategy/Analysis
                %p.benefit-description
                  Quality strategies with unparalleled analysis! Campaigns are
                  only as good as the data it generates, and how you read and
                  react to it. This is where Myrick excels.
            / BENEFIT 2
            .col-sm-6.col-md-4
              .benefit
                %span.benefit-icon.fa.fa-laptop{"data-animation" => "bounceIn"}
                %h4.benefit-title Websites
                %p.benefit-description
                  Modern designs with easy to maintain CMS's for lower
                  maintenance costs. Sites built with optimization in mind.
            .hidden-md.hidden-lg.clear
            / BENEFIT 3
            .col-sm-6.col-md-4
              .benefit
                %span.benefit-icon.fa.fa-print{"data-animation" => "bounceIn"}
                %h4.benefit-title Print
                %p.benefit-description
                  From business cards to 25' banners and everything in between.
                  Producing mail campaigns, brochures, presentation folders and
                  more all while using the most high quality printing
                  practices.
            .hidden-sm.clear
            / BENEFIT 4
            .col-sm-6.col-md-4
              .benefit
                %span.benefit-icon.fa.fa-rocket{"data-animation" => "bounceIn"}
                %h4.benefit-title SEO
                %p.benefit-description
                  Our SEO & PPC department work hand and hand with our website
                  department so you can hit the ground running. We use best
                  practices from Google, and are Google certified.
            .hidden-md.hidden-lg.clear
            / BENEFIT 5
            .col-sm-6.col-md-4
              .benefit
                %span.benefit-icon.fa.fa-crop{"data-animation" => "bounceIn"}
                %h4.benefit-title Graphic Design
                %p.benefit-description
                  Design in a way to draw attention and invoke a quality response or lead!
            / BENEFIT 6
            .col-sm-6.col-md-4
              .benefit
                %span.benefit-icon.fa.fa-hand-o-up{"data-animation" => "bounceIn"}
                %h4.benefit-title Digital Advertising
                %p.benefit-description
                  Re-Targeting, Digital Display, and IP Targeting! Narrow your
                  demographic by using one or many of the 750 plus different
                  household criteria you can choose from.
      / HOW IT WORKS
      %section#how-it-works.how-it-works-section.section
        .container-fluid
          %h2.section-heading.text-center How it Works
          .hiw-row.row
            / HOW IT WORKS - ITEM 1
            .col-sm-6.col-md-3{"data-animation" => "fadeIn"}
              .hiw-item
                {{ 'contents/step-1.jpg' | theme_image_tag: "class:hiw-item-picture" }}
                .hiw-item-text
                  %span.hiw-item-icon 1
                  %h4.hiw-item-title Contact Myrick
                  %p.hiw-item-description Call us, Tweet at us, post on our (FB Logo here)! Just reach out any way you can so we can get started Contact Us button (Directs down the page to the form) Call 800-571-1957 Email button 

            / HOW IT WORKS - ITEM 2
            .col-sm-6.col-md-3{"data-animation" => "fadeIn"}
              .hiw-item.even
                {{ 'contents/step-2.jpg' | theme_image_tag: "class:hiw-item-picture" }}
                .hiw-item-text
                  %span.hiw-item-icon 2
                  %h4.hiw-item-title Research & Strategize
                  %p.hiw-item-description We research your primary and secondary demographic, and then develop the strategy and message to reach them.
            .hidden-md.hidden-lg.clear
            / HOW IT WORKS - ITEM 3
            .col-sm-6.col-md-3{"data-animation" => "fadeIn"}
              .hiw-item
                {{ 'contents/step-3.jpg' | theme_image_tag: "class:hiw-item-picture" }}
                .hiw-item-text
                  %span.hiw-item-icon 3
                  %h4.hiw-item-title Execute & Manage 
                  %p.hiw-item-description Execute & manage the campaign. Adjusting the campaign if necessary based on the analytics is something Myrick prides itself on.
            / HOW IT WORKS - ITEM 4
            .col-sm-6.col-md-3{"data-animation" => "fadeIn"}
              .hiw-item.even
                {{ 'contents/step-4.jpg' | theme_image_tag: "class:hiw-item-picture" }}
                .hiw-item-text
                  %span.hiw-item-icon 4
                  %h4.hiw-item-title Reporting
                  %p.hiw-item-description Reporting is one of the most important steps we take with our clients. We go over these reports with you, what worked best and continue to move forward with those best practices.
      / TESTIMONIAL SLIDER
      %section#testimonial-slider.testimonial-slider-section.section-dark.section
        .section-background
          / IMAGE BACKGROUND
          .section-background-image.parallax{"data-stellar-ratio" => "0.4"}
            {{ 'backgrounds/testimonial-slider-bg.jpg' | theme_image_tag: "class:opacity-015" }}
        .container
          %h2.section-heading.text-center.hidden Trusted by Thousands
          .testimonial-slider-row.row
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
              %ul.testimonial-slider.rslides{"data-auto" => "false", "data-speed" => "800", "data-timeout" => "4000"}
                / TESTIMONIAL ITEM 2
                .testimonial-slide
                  %span.testimonial-ratings
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                  %blockquote.testimonial-quote
                    %p Fast, affordable and cares about the customer and their pockets, A+ service!
                  %cite.testimonial-cite George Vlahakis, TwiztID
                / TESTIMONIAL ITEM 3
                %li.testimonial-slide
                  %span.testimonial-ratings
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                  %blockquote.testimonial-quote
                    %p
                      Myrick Consulting is like having your own personal print
                      shop. The staff is personable, professional, and always
                      goes that extra mile to meet your every need. Not to
                      mention, the quality of all of their products is top
                      notch and the delivery times are untouchable. If you
                      need quality printed products at a remarkable price,
                      think Myrick Consulting. I do.
                  %cite.testimonial-cite Rico Mann, Parks Millican & Mann
                / TESTIMONIAL ITEM 4
                .testimonial-slide
                  %span.testimonial-ratings
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                    %span.fa.fa-star
                  %blockquote.testimonial-quote
                    %p
                      We have been dealing with Chris for a long time now and
                      would follow him anywhere. The quality and service has
                      been the best we have come across in our 30 years of
                      business by far!!!
                  %cite.testimonial-cite Alex Servellon, Audio Advisers Inc.
          /.sponsors-row{"data-animation" => "bounceIn"}
          /%img{:alt => "", :src => "images/contents/sponsor-1a.png"}/
          /%img{:alt => "", :src => "images/contents/sponsor-2a.png"}/
          /%img{:alt => "", :src => "images/contents/sponsor-3a.png"}/
          /%img{:alt => "", :src => "images/contents/sponsor-4a.png"}/
